		<h2>What are the shipping charges?</h2>
		<br/>

		<div align="justify" style="font-size: 12px; color: #333333">ShopKul.com
		does not charge any shipping charges if your total order amount is
		more than Rs. 100. Otherwise Rs. 30 are charged as shipping charges.</div>
		<br />


		<h2>What is the estimated delivery time?</h2>
		<br />
		<div align="justify" style="font-size: 12px; color: #333333">Delivery
		time estimates are mentioned along with each book may vary from 3
		working days to few weeks depending on the book.<br />
		<br />

		These delivery estimates are for areas which are serviced by reputed
		courier companies. Otherwise book is sent through registered post
		through Indian Postal Service and might take 1-2 weeks to reach its
		destination.<br />
		<br />
		Also, the delivery times mentioned do not apply to bulk orders.<br />
		<br />
		</div>
		<br />

		<h2>What about warranty and hidden costs (sales tax, octroi etc.)?</h2>

		<br />
		<div align="justify" style="font-size: 12px; color: #333333">There are
		no extra taxes, hidden costs or additional shipping charges. The price
		mentioned on page is final. Our prices are all inclusive. All taxes
		are included with the list prices.<br />
		<br />
		</div>
		<br />
		</div>
