		<br/>
		<div align="justify" style="font-size: 12px; color: #333333">If
		there's anything wrong with the book shipped by ShopKul.com, we will
		get the book picked up from your place and replace/refund your order.
		Please contact us through <a href="${request.contextPath}/contact">Contact Us</a> Form.</div>
		<br />

